com.asascience.ncsos.describesen

Class SOSDescribeProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.asascience.ncsos.describesen.SOSDescribeStation
      • com.asascience.ncsos.describesen.SOSDescribeProfile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SOSDescribeIF

    public class SOSDescribeProfile
extends SOSDescribeStation
implements SOSDescribeIF
    Handles Describe Sensor requests for Profile feature datasets. Describe Sensor requests to Profile datasets for response "sensorML/1.0.1" output the following xml subroots: *Description *Identification *Classification *Contact(s) *History *Positions (note the plural) *Component(s)
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    SCowan
